posts.post_title: breaking up T210 series 6 nr set, NOW considering want lists
posts.post_content:
I have 65 of the 66 T210 series 6 cards of the Blue Grass League. I lack Angermeier fielding. They average G to VG, 2 or 3 a bit short of that, several better, a few pretty nice. 

Here's a scan of the Stengel card.

[IMG]http://i78.photobucket.com/albums/j106/greatwake/T210OldMillWinchester300.jpg[/IMG]


I will not respond to messages sent through Net54. Please don't use it.

PLEASE us my email, [url]fwakefield1@comcast.net[/url] if you are interested.

Again, I will respond to direct emails to [url]fwakefield1@comcast.net[/url] 
I will not respond to posts or messages through Net54. I'm current with correspondence, so if you've not heard back from me it is because you used something other than the email address.

Here are the rest of the cards, by team. And it looks like I may well break these guys up and sell them individually. I have 3 lists already, and I think one more is on the way...
